OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter leaving woman in critical
OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,FA 30-year-old man has been charged
OL,8,Fwith attempted murder after a woman
OL,9,Fwas found injured at a home.
OL,11,FNottinghamshire Police were called to
OL,12,FBley Avenue in East Leake on the
OL,13,Fafternoon of Tuesday after reports a
OL,14,Fwoman had suffered serious injuries.
OL,16,FThe woman, in her late-20s, has been
OL,17,Ftaken to hospital due to her critical
OL,18,Fcondition.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
