OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1775315484
OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter leaving woman in critical
OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,FShaquel Kerr, 30, of Pamela Road,
OL,8,FBirmingham, has been taken into
OL,9,Fcustody.
OL,11,FDetective Chief Inspector Les Charlton
OL,12,Fsaid: "This was an isolated incident
OL,13,Finside a home but we understand
OL,14,Fresidents in the area may have been
OL,15,Fconcerned by the police presence.
OL,17,F"I hope they are reassured by our
OL,18,Finvestigation which has now seen a
OL,19,Fsuspect placed before the courts at
OL,20,Fthe earliest opportunity."
